ong>What comes next?</strong></h3><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Today, the era of Martha is endi=
ng. Things are speeding up. The world is no longer moving in just two direc=
tions at a time. </p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">As linear media (cable TV, magazines, books) =
are replaced by exponential media (TikTok, Twitter, Reddit) trends aren&#82=
17;t bifurcated, <strong>they&#8217;re moving in every direction&#8212;all =
at once.</strong></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Take this analysis of the GameStop phenomenon=
 <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM2OhSAMhZ_msrsGEEQWLGYzr2=
H4qUqugAGciW8_qItJmjbpSXvaz-oKS8qn2lOp6EpTPXdQEX7LBrVCRkeBPHmnyEDHnjOJnGKOj=
